show.description: Li Xiaoyun, framed and imprisoned by the four major clans, trained under the Black Emperor for five years. Upon his release, he returned to uncover the mastermind behind his downfall. Learning his sister Li Xue was alive and being bullied, he set out on a path of vengeance.
